4_-bodrum_-turkey.en.mfa|title=From Rep. of Turkey Ministry of Foreign Affairs|website=Republic of Turkey Ministry of Foreign Affairs|accessdate=25 August 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| December 24, 2014 || {{flag|Ukraine}} || [[Kiev]] || Opening of the first Turkic Council Regional Diaspora Center<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.turkkon.org/en-US/turkic-council-regional-diaspora-center-is-opened-on-24-december-2014-in-kyiv/301/352/352/1123|title=T\u00fcrk Dili Konu\u015fan \u00dclkeler \u0130\u015fbirli\u011fi Konseyi|website=Turkkon.org|accessdate=25 August 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| September 11, 2015 || {{flag|Kazakhstan}} || [[Astana]] || Fifth Turkic Council Summit, Cooperation in Media and Information\n|-\n| September 2, 2018 || {{flag|Kyrgyzstan}} || [[Cholpon Ata]] || Sixth Turkic Council Summit\n|-\n| October 15,  2019 || {{flag|Azerbaijan}} || [[Baku]] || Seventh Turkic Council Summit\n|-\n|}\n\n== List of Secretaries-General of the Turkic Council ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! No. !! Name !! Country of origin !! Took office !! Left office !! Note\n|-\n| 1 || '''[[Halil Ak\u0131nc\u0131]]''' || {{flag|Turkey}} || 3 October 2009 || 16 September 2014 || End of extended term\n|-\n| 2 || '''Ramil Hasanov''' || {{flag|Azerbaijan}} || 16 September 2014 || 3 September 2018 || End of extended term\n|-\n| 3 || '''Baghdad Amreyev''' || {{flag|Kazakhstan}} || 3 September 2018 ||  ||\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Azerbaijan - Turkic Council relations]]\n*[[List of Turkic dynasties and countries]]\n*[[List of international organizations based in Istanbul]]\n*[[World Turks Qurultai]]\n\n== Notes ==\n<references group=\"lower-alpha\"></references>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.turkkon.org/en-US/HomePage Official website]\n*[https://www.turk-pa.org/en/content/docs/other_docs/382_nakhchivan_agreement Text of the Nakhchivan Agreement]\n\n{{Regional organizations}}\n{{Economic Cooperation Organization}}\n{{Countries and languages lists}}\n{{Turkic topics}}\n\n